{"tid":1357590,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【幫手做主題分類】 連登重新定位:上環721熱門總匯","createTime":"2019-07-23T18:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T11:22:11.000Z","uid":90073,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ce769a34e4c998bb6b1b9fb2b458188d26130df5","tid":1357590,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:00:53.000Z","msg":"連登響反送中單野一路以黎既定位係咩?<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">係走在最前 要比所有人、比時代都要走到最前</span></span><br />\n好多人要屌都屌過<br />\n我都不嫌其煩再講多次<br />\n唔好再理何君堯<br />\n黑吃黑由佢地 我地唔洗理<br />\n元朗單野亦會有一般市民去跟去傳更加多既消息<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但係之後呢? 係咪就咁完左件事?</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地響連登要做既野就係要諗定下一步做咩</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">下一步:我地要還原基本步=針對返721</span></span><br />\n<br />\n小弟幫大家整理左部份圍繞721上環方面既熱門做主軸 其他大家可自己去搵:<br />\n1)［今次革命最基本既總綱領，亦最重要既初衷，無時間可以睇呢個，所以要置頂］<br />\n（帶風向）對準政權 做好文宣 臨時立會 HKSDF 光復香港 時代革命<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356721\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356721</a><br />\n<br />\n2)［想知721上環黑警失控、濫用暴力既進一步情況，可以深入了解，並進一步宣傳]<br />\n【文宣包】同我入黎！721西環宣言！上環36槍！文宣打包哂俾你<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356661\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356661</a><br />\n<br />\n３)［有更多時間想睇片，可以睇呢個］<br />\n上環721 Video 整合 (粗略)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348465\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348465</a><br />\n<br />\n４)［要明白警方721當時既心理狀態，我地先可以再調整文攻武鬥既策略]<br />\n「721」當晚啲狗已經崩潰晒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357216\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357216</a><br />\n<br />\n5)［三軍未動，糧草先行，我地可以聽下物資組巴絲有咩建議］<br />\n【 發夢認真post】 物資 救援 車手 入嚟唔該<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357265\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357265</a><br />\n<br />\n6)［知己知彼，要兼顧返我方目前既補給後勤：極為惡劣，尤其好多人用完即棄／唔自備］<br />\n［推上熱門］一定要回收頭盔，極珍貴<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344143\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344143</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩可唔可以揾物資巴絲係尾班車個陣拎走MTR啲錢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dmCjPS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dmCjPS</a><br />\n<br />\n下次全撚部物資跟身，人人袋d<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352356\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352356</a><br />\n<br />\n有鑑於物資方面成日俾人忽略，我會多SHARE呢方面既幾個POST，從而帶出：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">我地唔係唔夠錢，依家係俾黑警BLOCK晒水路，我地要盡可能回收物資＋開拓新入貨源</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94647d1c8f870c1927c907a9e88aeb900950b1ec","tid":1357590,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:04:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44dd7305364439974d3b1a782ede9c4803c97d14","tid":1357590,"uid":263945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7d6dc87b98690be6a8d68b783b3ff85b2d5e711","tid":1357590,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:05:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8687be21f216ace305c844985b0efee57ffc70fe","tid":1357590,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:05:21.000Z","msg":"<code>幫手推有用post</code>"},{"pid":"bafd95678143103d95911d2e589109e47c3de79e","tid":1357590,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8687be21f216ace305c844985b0efee57ffc70fe","tid":1357590,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:05:21.000Z","msg":"<code>幫手推有用post</code>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:08:27.000Z","msg":"感謝大大"},{"pid":"1c2838c0eb8f1609cb1bef75253fe8b676e8adf2","tid":1357590,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:09:06.000Z","msg":"依家太多ＰＯＳＴ<br />\n好容易搵唔返<br />\n只能夠幫幫大家易Ｄ搵到重點"},{"pid":"9a0a9bdec4675cb9cef5d6e0356b46cc2c5be1d0","tid":1357590,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07